\c 13
\s Ukubusa kukaAbhiya
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wetshumi lesificaminwembili wenkosi uJerobhowamu uAbhiya wasesiba yinkosi phezu kukaJuda\x + 1 Kho. 15.1,2.\x*.
\v 2 Wabusa iminyaka emithathu eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguMikhaya indodakazi kaUriyeli\x + 11.20. 1 Kho. 15.2.\x* weGibeya\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*. Kwasekusiba khona impi phakathi kukaAbhiya loJerobhowamu\x + 1 Kho. 15.7.\x*.
\v 3 UAbhiya wasehlela impi elebutho lamaqhawe empi, amadoda akhethiweyo azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amane. UJerobhowamu wasehlela impi ukumelana laye elamadoda akhethiweyo azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisificaminwembili, amaqhawe alamandla\x + 14.10. Hlu. 20.22. 1 Sam. 17.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 UAbhiya wasesima entabeni iZemarayimi\x + 13.19. Josh. 18.22.\x* esentabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x* wathi: Ngizwa Jerobhowamu, loIsrayeli wonke!
\v 5 Kakusikwenu yini ukwazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli yanika uDavida umbuso phezu kukaIsrayeli phakade\x + 2 Sam. 7.12,13,16.\x*, kuye lakumadodana akhe ngesivumelwano setshwayi\x + Nani 18.19.\x*?
\v 6 Kodwa uJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati, inceku kaSolomoni indodana kaDavida, wasukuma wavukela inkosi yakhe\x + 1 Kho. 11.26. 12.19,20.\x*.
\v 7 Kwasekubuthana kuye abantu abayize\x + Hlu. 9.4.\x*, abantwana bakaBheliyali\x + Dute. 13.13.\x*, baziqinisa ukumelana loRehobhowamu indodana kaSolomoni, uRehobhowamu esesengumfana njalo ebuthakathaka ngenhliziyo engemelane labo\x + 12.13. 2 Kho. 2.23.\x*.
\v 8 Khathesi-ke lina lithi lizamelana lombuso weN\nd kosi\nd* esandleni samadodana kaDavida\x + 1 Lan. 29.23.\x*; futhi lilixuku elikhulu, kodwa lilamathole egolide\x + 1 Kho. 12.28.\x* uJerobhowamu alenzela wona abe ngonkulunkulu.
\v 9 Kalibaxotshanga yini abapristi beN\nd kosi\nd*, amadodana kaAroni, lamaLevi, lazenzela abapristi njengezizwe zelizwe\x + 11.14,15. 1 Kho. 12.31.\x*? Loba ngubani ozegcwalisa isandla sakhe ngejongosi, ithole lenkomo, lezinqama eziyisikhombisa\x + Eks. 29.1.\x* uba ngumpristi wabangeyisibo onkulunkulu\x + Jer. 5.7. Dute. 32.21.\x*.
\v 10 Kodwa thina, iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu wethu, kasiyidelanga; labapristi abayikhonzayo iN\nd kosi\nd* bangamadodana kaAroni, lamaLevi asemsebenzini\x + 1 Kho. 15.3.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo bayahlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* ikuseni ngekuseni lentambama ngentambama iminikelo yokutshiswa\x + 2.4.\x* lempepha elephunga elimnandi\x + 2.4.\x*; lokulungisa izinkwa etafuleni elihlambulukileyo\x + 4.19. 1 Lan. 9.32.\x*\x + 2.4.\x*, lokulumathisa uluthi lwesibane lwegolide lezibane zalo\x + 4.20.\x* kusihlwa ngakusihlwa\x + Eks. 27.20,21. Levi 24.2-4.\x*. Ngoba thina sigcina umlindo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu\x + Nani 1.53.\x*, kodwa lina liyidelile.
\v 12 Ngakho khangelani, uNkulunkulu ulathi eyinhloko, labapristi bakhe belempondo zokukhalisa ukuhlaba umkhosi bemelene lani\x + Nani 10.9.\x*. Bantwana bakoIsrayeli, lingalwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, ngoba kaliyikuphumelela\x + Seb. 5.39.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kodwa uJerobhowamu wayebhodise abacathameli ukuthi beze bengasemva kwabo. Ngakho babephambi kukaJuda, labacathameli bengemva kwabo\x + 20.22. Josh. 8.9. Hlu. 9.34. 20.29.\x*.
\v 14 Lapho uJuda ephenduka, khangela-ke, impi yayimelene labo ngaphambili langemuva; basebekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, labapristi bakhalisa izimpondo\x + 13.12.\x*,
\v 15 labantu bakoJuda bamemeza; kwasekusithi ekumemezeni kwabantu bakoJuda uNkulunkulu watshaya oJerobhowamu loIsrayeli wonke phambi kukaAbhiya loJuda\x + 14.12.\x*.
\v 16 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebaleka phambi kobuso bukaJuda, uNkulunkulu wasebanikela esandleni sabo\x + 16.8. Hlu. 3.28.\x*.
\v 17 UAbhiya labantu bakhe basebebatshaya ngokutshaya okukhulu; kwasekusiwa ababuleweyo koIsrayeli, amadoda akhethiweyo azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amahlanu.
\v 18 Ngokunjalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli bathotshiswa ngalesosikhathi, labantwana bakoJuda baba lamandla ngoba beyama eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + 14.11. 16.7,8. Isa. 10.20. 31.1. 1 Lan. 5.20.\x*.
\v 19 UAbhiya wasexotshana loJerobhowamu, wathumba imizi kuye, iBhetheli lemizana yayo\x + 15.8. 17.2. 1 Kho. 12.30.\x*, leJeshana lemizana yayo, leEfroni lemizana yayo\x + Josh. 15.9. 18.23.\x*.
\v 20 UJerobhowamu akabe esaba lamandla ensukwini zikaAbhiya\x + 1 Lan. 29.14.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimtshaya\x + 1 Sam. 25.38.\x*, wafa\x + 1 Kho. 14.20.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Kodwa uAbhiya waziqinisa, wazithathela abafazi abalitshumi lane, wazala amadodana angamatshumi amabili lambili, lamadodakazi alitshumi lesithupha\x + 12.13.\x*.
\v 22 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAbhiya, lezindlela zakhe, lamazwi akhe, kubhaliwe ezindabeni zomprofethi uIdo\x + 9.29.\x*.